==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Congius
<hw>Con"gi*us</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Roman Antiq.)</fld> <def>A liquid measure containing
about three quarts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A gallon, or four quarts.</def>
<altsp>[Often abbreviated to <asp>cong.</asp>]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Conglaciate</ent>⟦br⟧
